Public IP address ranges in Yandex Cloud
Written by
Yandex Cloud
Updated at June 26, 2026
View in Markdown

For Yandex Cloud network resources, two types of public IP addresses are used:

Yandex Cloud resource IP addresses available to the customers, e.g., IP addresses of Compute Cloud VMs and database hosts.

IP addresses used by Yandex Cloud to enable its services, e.g., to record audit logs in Audit Trails.

